milestones.description: de Silva has broken the record for most sixes (18) in ODIs for SL, going past Madugalle's 16
Hashan Tillakaratne has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (50) in an innings in ODIs for SL, going past Roy Dias's 48
de Silva and Hashan Tillakaratne's 150-run partnership is SL's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 137 between de Silva and Mahanama
